Text: RE Im Leaving Enronthanks for including me in this notice I would like to wish you the very best in your new position and location Perhaps our paths will cross again Of course if I can ever be of assistance in any way please let me know Jim Original Message From mailto Sent None To KADDENCOM kaddencom WPPCorg Devon Kehoe TomO PAgov ernercom Subject Im Leaving Enron judy WPPORG MCIMAILCOM Date Fri Mar MessageID XMIMETrack Serialize by Router on ENEMTAEnronRelease December at PM MIMEVersion Contenttype textplain charsetusascii I am going to be the Senior Regulatory Counsel at ISO New England starting on April My last day in the Portland area will be March I enjoyed working with you and wish you the best of everything My new address will be Mary Hain Senior Regulatory Counsel ISO New England Inc One Sullivan Road Holyoke MA SONEcom
